[src:deck-ship/abaft-p04] presenting one of several standard shapes (square, triangle, or rectangle) and colors (red, green, white, orange, yellow, or black).
[src:deck-ship/abaft-p04] A sailing boat without overnight accommodation, sometimes with a small cabin, used for pleasure sailing.
[src:deck-ship/abaft-p04] Exactly ahead; directly ahead; directly in front.
[src:deck-ship/abaft-p04] " ceremony at sea celebrated discharge of the debt.
[src:deck-ship/abaft-p04] Not moving (used only when a vessel is afloat and neither tied up nor anchored).
