[src:deck-ship/abaft-p07] An unexpected delay time during a voyage often spent at anchor or in a harbor.
[src:deck-ship/abaft-p07] It is usually caused by bad weather, equipment failure, or needed maintenance.
[src:deck-ship/abaft-p07] To bring a vessel into the wind and hold her stationary.
